urlLink DSM Tapes   Duane Sheriff Ministries is out of Oklahoma. I met a truck driver the other night while working security at a truck lot in Mt Pleasant. This truck driver was a believer in Christ and gave me four tapes that he orders.  This man gets 200 tapes per month or thereabouts and when he is driving over the road he listens to these teaching tapes.  I can not tell you how blessed I was just after listening to one of these tapes on Faith.  I want to encourage each of you that are reading this to think about blessing yourself by filling your mind and soul and spirit with the teaching ministry that this man has to offer.  God bless